---
title: Loaded Mexican Corn Fritter Bowl with Garlic Rice, Guac & Sour Cream
description: These gloriously bright fritters are both crunchy and sweet, and are set off perfectly by an A-team of tangy sour cream, guacamole and salsa. If you fancy it, you could also break out your favourite hot sauce for these bad boys!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/loaded-mexican-corn-fritter-bowl-ef2ffe01.jpg
